---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Navigation from "../../components/Navigation.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout title="Why I Started Writing">
  <Navigation />

  <main id="main-content" class="flex-1 max-w-[72ch] mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24 flex flex-col gap-12 font-sans">
    
    <!-- Article Header -->
    <header class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <div class="flex gap-2 text-xs text-[#71717A] font-mono">
        <span>Essay</span>
        <span>·</span>
        <span>July 2026</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-medium text-[#FAFAFA] tracking-tight leading-tight">
        Why I Started Writing
      </h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#A1A1AA] italic">
        "Build things that still make sense a decade later."
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Article Content -->
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 text-[#FAFAFA] text-base leading-[1.7] tracking-tight font-normal">
      <p>
        Software engineers build tools that resolve immediate needs.
        We write code to automate systems and coordinate data.
        However, coding is only part of the engineering process.
        The other half consists of structured thinking.
      </p>
      
      <p>
        Writing is how I organize my thinking.
        Most articles begin as questions that arise during study.
        By writing, I force myself to explain complex architectural components.
        If I cannot write a simple explanation, I do not understand the system.
      </p>

      <p>
        Documenting what I learn creates a record of progress.
        It turns lessons into permanent assets that I can refer to later.
        This practice compounds over time, making future builds cleaner.
        The goal is to communicate with clarity and humility.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Article Footer: Network of Knowledge -->
    <footer class="flex flex-col gap-8 border-t border-[rgba(255,255,255,0.08)] pt-12 mt-8">
      
      <!-- Related Links -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 text-sm">
        
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h4 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-medium">Further Reading</h4>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <li>
              <a href="/writing/the-kind-of-engineer-i-want-to-become" class="text-[#2563EB] hover:underline">
                The Kind of Engineer I Want to Become
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <h4 class="text-xs text-[#71717A] uppercase tracking-wider font-medium">Referenced Books</h4>
          <ul class="flex flex-col gap-2">
            <li>
              <a href="/reading" class="text-[#2563EB] hover:underline">
                The Pragmatic Programmer
              </a>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

    </footer>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
